These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
House: colonial, farmhouse, craftsman, townhouse, ranch-style, futuristic, cottage
There are 7 different nationalities: argentine, australian, canadian, chinese, mexican, nigerian, thai
 1. the townhouse house is on the left of the chinese##1
 2. the mexican is the townhouse house##1
 3. the cottage house is on the right of the futuristic house##1
 4. the canadian is on the right of the nigerian##1
 5. the craftsman house is in the middle##1
 6. the argentine is on the far left##1
 7. the ranch-style house is the argentine##1
 8. the colonial house is on the right of the nigerian##1
 9. the canadian is on the left of the australian##1
10. the chinese is on the left of the craftsman house##1
11. the cottage house is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| House           | ranch-style | townhouse | farmhouse | craftsman | colonial | futuristic | cottage |
| Nationality   | argentine    | mexican   | chinese      | nigerian | canadian    | australian    | thai         |

