.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: june, november, july, october, april, january, may
The people have 7 different jobs:  bartender, freelancer, mechanic, photographer, scientist, teacher, writer
 1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the writer##1
 3. the freelancer is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 5. the bartender is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 6. the mechanic is on the right of the freelancer##1
 7. the freelancer is on the left of the mechanic##1
 8. the freelancer is on the right of the photographer##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is the photographer##1
10. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the bartender##1
11. the photographer is in the middle##1
12. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Birthday   | november | april     | july  | january       | june       | may  | october   |
| Job    | teacher  | bartender | writer | photographer | freelancer | mechanic | scientist |

