.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: horror, drama, adventure, western, action, comedy, superhero
There are 7 different nationalities: argentine, australian, egyptian, indian, indonesian, nigerian, thai
 1. the person watching action movies is the australian##1
 2. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
 3. the nigerian is on the right of the egyptian##1
 4. the argentine is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
 5. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
 6. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
 7. the egyptian is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the nigerian##1
 9. the person watching adventure movies is the indonesian##1
10. the indonesian is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
11. the thai is the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | superhero     | western     | adventure      | drama | action      | horror     |
| Nationality   | indian | egyptian | nigerian | indonesian | thai | australian | argentine |

