.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
There are 7 different nationalities: british, australian, brazilian, german, spanish, french, turkish
7 different pets are kept: dog, fish, frog, goldfish, guinea-pig, horse, snake
 1. the australian is the owner of the snake##1
 2. the owner of the fish is on the right of the spanish##1
 3. the owner of the horse is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 5. the owner of the guinea-pig is the french##1
 6. the spanish is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 7. the owner of the horse is on the left of the turkish##1
 8. the brazilian is on the right of the australian##1
 9. the german is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
10. the spanish is on the right of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Nationality   | australian | brazilian | french     | german | turkish | spanish | british |
| Pet     | snake   | frog    | guinea-pig | horse     | dog         | goldfish     | fish        |

