.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-6::.
There are 7 different nationalities: dutch, mexican, polish, indian, russian, egyptian, italian
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, quad-bike, ship, skateboard, tram, trike
 1. the egyptian is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 2. the dutch is the person driving the bus##1
 3. the russian is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 4. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 5. the person driving the trike is on the right of the italian##1
 6. the egyptian is on the left of the dutch##1
 7. the indian is in the middle##1
 8. the polish is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 9. the mexican is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
10. the polish is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Nationality    | polish | egyptian   | dutch | indian | italian  | russian | mexican |
| Transport   | ship   | skateboard | bus | tram     | jet-ski | trike | quad-bike   |

