.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cycling, climbing, handball, tennis, weightlifting, snowboarding, skateboarding
The people use 7 different means of transport: boat, jet-ski, motorbike, roller, skateboard, snowmobile, trike
 1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person driving the roller##1
 4. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 6. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 7. the person driving the boat is the person who's sport is handball##1
 8. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
10. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Sport   | cycling  | skateboarding | tennis | weightlifting | snowboarding     | climbing | handball |
| Transport     | snowmobile | roller      | trike | motorbike    | skateboard | jet-ski   | boat  |

