.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-9::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: emerald, green, aquamarine, white, turquise, yellow, amber
The people use 7 different means of transport: airplane, bike, boat, jet-ski, subway, tram, van
 1. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
