 3. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
 4. the person driving the airplane is in the middle##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is the person who likes emerald##1
 6. the person driving the subway is the person who likes yellow##1
 7. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
 8. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 9. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who likes green##1
10. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
11. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2     |   3    |    4     |   5    |     6      |   7    |
| Color        | green | emerald | aquamarine | white     | yellow | amber | turquise |
| Transport   | tram | jet-ski  | van    | airplane | subway | bike       | boat   |

