.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-15::.
There 7 different types of food: blueberry, cucumber, grapes, pomegranate, radish, raspberry, tomato
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, azalea, balloon-flower, daisy, sunflower, iris, begonia
 1. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
 2. the person eating radish is on the far right##1
 3. the person eating raspberry is the person who growsazalea##1
 4. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 5. the person who growsiris is on the far right##1
 6. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
 7. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
 8. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
 9. the person who growssunflower is in the middle##1
10. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
11. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |   2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |     6     |      7       |
| Food    | cucumber | grapes | tomato     | blueberry | pomegranate | raspberry | radish       |
| Flower   | amaryllis | daisy | balloon-flower | sunflower     | begonia  | azalea  | iris |

