 8. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 9. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
10. the person playing canasta is the person who's hobby is singing##1
11. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
